   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Purpose     : Global using directives for all Razor components in this
                 project.  Namespaces listed here are automatically available
                 in every .razor file without explicit @using statements.
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Changes     :
     - 1.0.0  2026-03-13  Initial implementation.
     - 1.1.0  2026-03-23  Added PageTemplatesV2 namespace so TableSettingsPageV2
                           and other V2 components under Components/ can use
                           PageTemplateV2 without per-file @using declarations.
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Notes       :
     - Blazor automatically processes this file; do not add markup or
       directives other than @using, @inject, and similar non-render items.
     - Add new project namespaces here to avoid repetitive @using lines
       across individual page files.
   ===========================================================================
*@

